OL,3,CBoy jailed for life for hammer attack
OL,4,Con sleeping pupils at private school
OL,6,FA public schoolboy who attacked two
OL,7,Fsleeping students and a teacher with
OL,8,Fhammers at a boarding school has been
OL,9,Fjailed for life.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,12,Ffor legal reasons, had been a pupil at
OL,13,FBlundell's School, in Tiverton, Devon,
OL,14,Fwhen he assaulted his dorm-mates and
OL,15,Fhousemaster in the early hours of 9
OL,16,FJune last year.
