OL,6,F"It is impossible to say when you will
OL,7,Fcease to be dangerous."
OL,9,FSpeaking after the court hearing,
OL,10,Fsenior investigating officer,
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent James Dowler,
OL,12,Fsaid: "This incident had a lasting
OL,13,Feffect not only on the victims and
OL,14,Ftheir families but on the whole school
OL,15,Fcommunity and those who were present
OL,16,Fthat night."
