OL,6,FWhen he entered the bedroom, he saw a
OL,7,Fsilhouetted figure standing in the
OL,8,Froom who turned towards him and struck
OL,9,Fhim over the head with a hammer six
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,12,FThe court heard both boys suffered
OL,13,Fskull fractures, as well as injuries
OL,14,Fto their ribs, spleen, a punctured
OL,15,Flung and internal bleeding.
OL,17,FThe two boys were rushed to hospital,
OL,18,Fand the court heard they only survived
OL,19,Fdue to the prompt arrival of
OL,20,Fparamedics and the skilful work of the
OL,21,Fdoctors and surgeons.
