OL,6,FJames Dawes KC, prosecuting,
OL,7,Fpreviously told the jury both boys are
OL,8,Fliving with the "long-term
OL,9,Fconsequences" of the attack but have
OL,10,Fno memory of the incident.
OL,12,FThe offender told police under
OL,13,Finterview that he accepted carrying
OL,14,Fout the attacks - but denied attempted
OL,15,Fmurder, claiming that he had been
OL,16,Fsleepwalking after watching horror
OL,17,Ffilms.
