OL,6,FDuring the two-month trial, the court
OL,7,Fheard the boy was wearing just his
OL,8,Fboxer shorts and was "on a mission" to
OL,9,Fprotect himself from a zombie
OL,10,Fapocalypse when he carried out the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FJurors heard from several sleep
OL,14,Fexperts who offered clinical advice on
OL,15,Fthe likelihood of the offender being
OL,16,Fable to carry out such an attack while
OL,17,Fbeing in a state of sleep.
