OL,6,F"These are deliberate actions and he
OL,7,Frained blows down on their unprotected
OL,8,Fsleeping heads with heavy hammers,"
OL,9,Fsaid Mr Dawes.
OL,11,FIn a victim personal impact statement,
OL,12,Fone of the 16-year-old victim's family
OL,13,Fthanked everyone who assisted in their
OL,14,Fson's recovery.
