OL,6,F"The police and the prosecution team
OL,7,Fhave helped us navigate this horrific
OL,8,Fcase with the utmost professionalism
OL,9,Fand compassion. Their thoroughness and
OL,10,Fattention to detail in the
OL,11,Finvestigation has been truly
OL,12,Fimpressive," they said.
OL,14,FThe 17-year-old victim's family added:
OL,15,F"I am looking forward to my family
OL,16,Fmoving on now that the trial is over,
OL,17,Fand I hope my son will continue his
OL,18,Frecovery and have a good future ahead."
