OL,6,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,7,FDetective Superintendent James Dowler,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was an unprovoked attack
OL,9,Fon two schoolboys as they slept in
OL,10,Ftheir beds. The assaults were both
OL,11,Fbrutal and savage and I have no doubt
OL,12,Fthat his intent was to kill.
OL,14,F"Our detectives worked tirelessly to
OL,15,Fprove that the offender had indeed
OL,16,Fbeen fully conscious when committing
OL,17,Fthis horrendous attack - which had
OL,18,Fbeen months in the planning.
