OL,6,FHe added: "I want to thank the victims
OL,7,Fand their families for their
OL,8,Fcontinuous support throughout this
OL,9,Ftrial and to the fellow pupils and
OL,10,Fparamedics who were present on the
OL,11,Fnight of the attack and offered life-
OL,12,Fsaving assistance to the casualties.
OL,14,F"I hope that the conclusion of the
OL,15,Fcase allows the victims and their
OL,16,Ffamilies space to move on in their
OL,17,Fyoung lives as they work to put these
OL,18,Fhorrific events behind them."
