OL,6,FIn a statement issued following the
OL,7,Fhearing the school's head teacher Bart
OL,8,FWielenga said he is "tremendously
OL,9,Fproud" of how the school's community
OL,10,Fresponded to the attacks.
OL,12,FHe added: "I have been very clear with
OL,13,Fthe pupils that this is not an
OL,14,Fincident we whisper about or have to
OL,15,Fbe ashamed of. It is part of our
OL,16,Fnarrative, our shared story. We are
OL,17,Fallowed to talk about it openly and we
OL,18,Fcan express our emotions safely.
