OL,6,F"I would like to record my thanks too
OL,7,Fto the emergency services who arrived
OL,8,Fon the scene so quickly and who
OL,9,Fhandled a difficult situation with
OL,10,Fsuch compassion and expertise. The
OL,11,Fsurgeons who treated the boys in the
OL,12,Fimmediate aftermath were heroic and
OL,13,Fthe care the boys received has been
OL,14,Fexcellent.
OL,16,F"Before and during the trial we have
OL,17,Fcontinued to work closely with the
OL,18,Fpolice, and I am grateful for the open
OL,19,Fand supportive relationship that has
OL,20,Fbeen formed between them and the
OL,21,FBlundell's team."
